ba1dd7127ba2d08101ba95dcdb500c9c43c","tid":1799922,"uid":69231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oDTZcgh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoDTZcgh.jpg&h=567378f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港律師會也公開表態，對於政府倉促提出草案感到遺憾和不合理，香港律師會會長何君堯說，「現時因應議員死亡或是辭職而舉行的補選制度一向行之有效，政制和內地事務局意圖更改這重要的制度，卻不在草案刊憲之前進行全面的諮詢對此律師會表示遺憾。」<br />\n<br />\n律師會要求擱置草案，馬上進行諮詢民意，何君堯說，「政府當局的建議將對香港的選舉制度做出重大的改變，並影響市民在基本法68條中享有的選舉的權利，香港的選民理應有機會討論這些建議並向當局提供意見。所以我們的結論就是政府應該擱置草案。」<br />\n<br />\n何妖個陣正常咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d34dc813ddcfb9170d5c006673afed71ab1bc4b","tid":1799922,"uid":69231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:44:47.000Z","msg":"2012<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sFE9zvQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsFE9zvQ.jpg&h=de61851f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n刻骨銘心 相信喚醒唔少同我一樣既90後"},{"pid":"e467f83cc887a33d3e2fe3484e58d5d3113b4ee5","tid":1799922,"uid":92002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:46:37.000Z","msg":"你錯過了保衛天星碼頭<br />\n你錯過了包圍禮賓府<br />\n你錯過了反世貿<br />\n<br />\n宅女，上街吧！<br />\n這個政府靠得過嗎？<br />\n宅女，上街吧！<br />\n你要未來繼續任由人魚肉嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1ce0c0167ebaa5af3ce4fd7107be7ba581f0e1","tid":1799922,"uid":69231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:48:54.000Z","msg":"2013<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wZNZWLw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwZNZWLw.jpg&h=6f71e8ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a779ccbbee47f4f8c4085ae9e6d98d3211cd15a","tid":1799922,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49a1aa668bf1676b90388aadf5a0ba2f1eea8491","tid":1799922,"uid":69231,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:25:57.000Z","msg":"反高鐵咁就十年 時間真係好快<br 